# 测试 file-service 图片上传功能

### 1. 测试 file-service 健康检查
GET http://localhost:12647/health

### 2. 测试获取产品图片上传URL (需要JWT token)
POST http://localhost:12647/api/files/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "fileName": "test-image.jpg",
  "fileSize": 1024000,
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
  "category": "product"
}

### 3. 测试通过 product-service 代理获取上传URL
POST http://localhost:12648/api/images/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "fileName": "test-image.jpg",
  "fileSize": 1024000,
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg"
}

